nodes.title: Note - Input video
widgets_values:
To avoid controlnet rendering the background of the video, use Runway to create a green screen video and use it as input. You can do it with a free account. https://runwayml.com/

frame_load_cap: Max number of frames. Set to 16 to 60 for fast testing. Set to higher values for final generation.

nodes.title: Note - LoRA
widgets_values:
# add_detail.safetensors
https://civitai.com/models/58390/detail-tweaker-lora-lora
- Increase background details. Increase strength if you don't see a background.

nodes.title: Note - Detailer
widgets_values:
- crop_factor is the scale factor to the detected bbox for crop. 2.5 seems to be min without causing issue.
- masking mode: combine neighboring frames results in a smaller mask. Important for not cropping the arms.
